{
  "id": "68ad90d9f797a8e61c5ee595",
  "title": "読書する人が主人公の話",
  "created": 1756205276,
  "updated": 1772273942,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68ad90d9f797a8e61c5ee595",
      "text": "読書する人が主人公の話",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1756205276,
      "updated": 1756205276
    },
    {
      "id": "68ad90dc0000000000d50be2",
      "text": "\t[京極堂シリーズ]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1756205276,
      "updated": 1756205284
    },
    {
      "id": "68ad90e50000000000d50be4",
      "text": "\t[税金で買った本]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1756205285,
      "updated": 1756205294
    },
    {
      "id": "68ad91320000000000d50be6",
      "text": "\t[R.O.D]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1756205363,
      "updated": 1756207137
    },
    {
      "id": "68ad98220000000000d3b44e",
      "text": "\t[図書館戦争]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1756207138,
      "updated": 1756219244
    },
    {
      "id": "68adc78f000000000023a6bd",
      "text": "\t\t読書はしてないか[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1756219279,
      "updated": 1756219283
    },
    {
      "id": "68adf2370000000000a7193f",
      "text": "\t[ネバーエンディング・ストーリー]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1756230200,
      "updated": 1756230200
    },
    {
      "id": "68adf2380000000000a71940",
      "text": "\t\t読むというか入るというか笑[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1756230200,
      "updated": 1756230206
    },
    {
      "id": "68ad90de0000000000d50be3",
      "text": " [戦う司書]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1756205278,
      "updated": 1756380661
    },
    {
      "id": "68b03df60000000000b3d043",
      "text": "  過去の日記に書いてあったけど内容忘れたな、、[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1756380663,
      "updated": 1756380676
    },
    {
      "id": "68b0556e0000000000fe8437",
      "text": " [舟を編む]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1756386669,
      "updated": 1756386774
    },
    {
      "id": "68b03dec0000000000b3d042",
      "text": "  とてもおすすめ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1756380653,
      "updated": 1756391241
    },
    {
      "id": "68b06741000000000092b221",
      "text": " [本好きの下剋上 司書になるために手段は選んでいられません]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1756391234,
      "updated": 1772273681
    },
    {
      "id": "69a2c012000000000069652b",
      "text": "  本がほぼない世界に転生したので紙を作るところから始める",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772273682,
      "updated": 1772273885
    },
    {
      "id": "69a2c0060000000000696529",
      "text": " [犬とハサミは使いよう]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772273671,
      "updated": 1772273891
    },
    {
      "id": "69a2c074000000000069652d",
      "text": "  好きな本が完結する前に死にそうになり死にたくないと思っていたら犬になった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772273780,
      "updated": 1772273892
    }
  ]
}